 # Splunk Alert Investigation â€“ Failed Login Attempts

## Alert Description
Multiple failed login attempts detected from a single IP address.

## Investigation Steps
1. Identify the source IP
2. Check number of attempts
3. Review affected user accounts
4. Correlate with successful logins
5. Check geolocation (if available)

## SPL Example
index=security action=failure
| stats count by src_ip user

## MITRE ATT&CK
- T1110: Brute Force

## Outcome
This activity may indicate a brute force attack and
should be escalated if thresholds are exceeded.
